{"book": 23, "chapter": 66, "sections": [{"type": "heading", "heading": "耶和華審判萬民"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "天是我的座位；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "地是我的腳凳。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們要為我造何等的殿宇？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "哪裏是我安息的地方呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說：這一切都是我手所造的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "所以就都有了。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "但我所看顧的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "就是虛心痛悔、"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因我話而戰兢的人。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 假冒為善的宰牛，好像殺人，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "獻羊羔，好像打折狗項，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "獻供物，好像獻豬血，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "燒乳香，好像稱頌偶像。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這等人揀選自己的道路，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "心裏喜悅行可憎惡的事。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我也必揀選迷惑他們的事，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使他們所懼怕的臨到他們；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為我呼喚，無人答應；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我說話，他們不聽從；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "反倒行我眼中看為惡的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "揀選我所不喜悅的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們因耶和華言語戰兢的人當聽他的話："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們的弟兄－就是恨惡你們，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因我名趕出你們的，曾說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "願耶和華得榮耀，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使我們得見你們的喜樂；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "但蒙羞的究竟是他們！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "有喧嘩的聲音出自城中！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "有聲音出於殿中！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "是耶和華向仇敵施行報應的聲音！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 錫安未曾劬勞就生產，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "未覺疼痛就生出男孩。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "國豈能一日而生？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "民豈能一時而產？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為錫安一劬勞便生下兒女，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這樣的事誰曾聽見？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "誰曾看見呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說：我既使她臨產，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "豈不使她生產呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你的神說：我既使她生產，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "豈能使她閉胎不生呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們愛慕耶路撒冷的"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "都要與她一同歡喜快樂；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們為她悲哀的"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "都要與她一同樂上加樂；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "使你們在她安慰的懷中吃奶得飽，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使他們得她豐盛的榮耀，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "猶如擠奶，滿心喜樂。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我要使平安延及她，好像江河，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使列國的榮耀延及她，如同漲溢的河。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們要從中享受；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們必蒙抱在肋旁，搖弄在膝上。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "母親怎樣安慰兒子，我就照樣安慰你們；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們也必因耶路撒冷得安慰。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們看見，就心中快樂；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們的骨頭必得滋潤像嫩草一樣；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "而且耶和華的手向他僕人所行的必被人知道；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他也要向仇敵發惱恨。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "看哪，耶和華必在火中降臨；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他的車輦像旋風，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "以烈怒施行報應，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "以火焰施行責罰；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "因為耶和華在一切有血氣的人身上，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "必以火與刀施行審判；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "被耶和華所殺的必多。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "「那些分別為聖、潔淨自己的，進入園內跟在其中一個人的後頭，吃豬肉和倉鼠並可憎之物，他們必一同滅絕；這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "「我知道他們的行為和他們的意念。時候將到，我必將萬民萬族聚來，看見我的榮耀， "}, {"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我要顯神蹟在他們中間。逃脫的，我要差到列國去，就是到他施、普勒、拉弓的路德和土巴、雅完，並素來沒有聽見我名聲、沒有看見我榮耀遼遠的海島；他們必將我的榮耀傳揚在列國中。 "}, {"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們必將你們的弟兄從列國中送回，使他們或騎馬，或坐車，坐轎，騎騾子，騎獨峯駝，到我的聖山耶路撒冷，作為供物獻給耶和華，好像以色列人用潔淨的器皿盛供物奉到耶和華的殿中；這是耶和華說的。 "}, {"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說：我也必從他們中間取人為祭司，為利未人。」"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說：我所要造的新天新地，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "怎樣在我面前長存；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你們的後裔和你們的名字也必照樣長存。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "每逢月朔、安息日，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "凡有血氣的必來在我面前下拜。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們必出去觀看那些違背我人的屍首；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為他們的蟲是不死的；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們的火是不滅的；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "凡有血氣的都必憎惡他們。"}]}]}